      "para_id": "Q001115.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Inana and Lugal-emuš , En-metena , ruler of Lagaš , child of En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , built the E-muš , their beloved temple ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001115.11",
      "line_range": "11",
      "translation": "(iii 3) The personal god of En-metena , whose name was proclaimed by Inana , the builder of the E-muš , is Šul-MUŠxPA ."
    }
  ],
